*alsa-tools-1.0.3 (01 Mar 2004)

  01 Mar 2004; Martin Holzer <mholzer@gentoo.org> alsa-tools-1.0.3.ebuild:
  Version bumped.

  19 Feb 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  alsa-tools-0.9.0_rc1-r1.ebuild, alsa-tools-0.9.1.ebuild,
